newsitem.title: SPAIN: SOCCER-FEYENOORD CLOSE OUT TENERIFE FOR GOALLESS DRAW.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-FEYENOORD CLOSE OUT TENERIFE FOR GOALLESS DRAW.

text.p: Tenerife had to be content with a goalless draw despite pinning Feyenoord back for most of their UEFA Cup third round first leg game on Tuesday.
Both sides wasted chances in an entertaining first half but as the game went on the Spaniards took control and were kept out only by a mixture of bad luck and fine defending by the Dutch side.
Feyenoord had won their previous away leg 3-0 against another Spanish team, Espanyol.
